snippet.textDisplay:
I have watched this video too many times. And RANGABATI became my fav song these days. I have already saved this video in my computer. Really loved this song and wonderfully sang by Sona Mohapatra... But I just can't understand that why this song is facing so many controversies. The original singer was respected Jitendra Haripal. But I have never heard his name... That song has been almost vanished in this era. But I really feel proud that Sona Mohapatra gave a limelight to this song along with the original singer, respected Jitendra Haripal. And I really feel very proud that this Sambalpuri song has been added to  the MTV coke studio hit list. Why people can't see the positive side !!! 10000 likes for this song. 

And the Tamil Rap was acting like a catalyst here... Really awesome. 

What to say about Rituraj !! He is awesome. BUT... BANDE UTKALA JANANI is our State Anthem. And I feel we should respect our Anthem. Instaed of Rangabati, Bande Utkala Janani should come to the controversy. Because Anthem should not be rimixed , we should not make it rock or adding rap to it. 

Love u all...  Sona and Rituraj... Ram Sampath and other Band Artists...
